Breeze icon subset
==================

The navigation, quick-access, folder, desktop, documents, and home icons in
this directory are derived without modification from KDE Breeze Icons commit
f8d528544fae6b014033fb9ff5a9d2b888cb45b4.

Source: https://invent.kde.org/frameworks/breeze-icons
License: GNU Lesser General Public License version 3 or later
License text and artwork clarification: COPYING.breeze-icons

The SVG files are the preferred source. The matching ICO files contain
16, 20, 24, 32, and 48 pixel renderings generated from those SVG files for
Wine resources.
